unpublishedAction.name: create_expense_invoice
jsonPathKeys:
{...CreateExpenseForm.formData,
					name: "/",
					ref: get_next_number.data.result,
					type: ExpenseUtils.ex_type,
					journal_id: ExpenseUtils.ex_journal_id,
					invoice_line_ids: CreateExpenseForm.formData.invoice_line_ids.map(
						x => ({
							...x,
							account_id: ExpenseUtils.ex_account_id,
							product_uom_id: ExpenseUtils.ex_uom_id,
							tax_ids: x["vat_included"] ? [ExpenseUtils.ex_tax_id] : []
						})
					).map(({vat_included, ...otherAttrs}) => otherAttrs)
				}
